author: Fextralife
description:
Path of Exile 2 Ranger Starter Guide - How to Build a Ranger
In this Path of Exile 2 video, I'm going to be discussing how to play the Ranger class. This video is designed for new rangers out there. How to get off to the start with the Ranger class. Explaining some of the basic mechanics how to play. It is not an advanced build guide that's meant for end game or cool difficulty or anything like that.

Timestamps
0:00 - Path of Exile 2 Early Access Ranger Guide
0:22 - Ranger Playstyles
2:17 - Ranger Passive Skill Tree
3:13 - Stats
5:28 - Ranger skills
10:32 - Ascendency Class 
11:32 - Final Thoughts
